 change regarding nullable status if the developer doesn't make it explicit.\r\n\r\nThanks!","author_association":"NONE","reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/bcit-ci/CodeIgniter/issues/comments/406875246/reactions","total_count":0,"+1":0,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":0,"rocket":0,"eyes":0},"performed_via_github_app":null,"event":"commented","actor":{"login":"mikifus","id":2385163,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjIzODUxNjM=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/2385163?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/mikifus","html_url":"https://github.com/mikifus","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/mikifus/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/mikifus/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/mikifus/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/mikifus/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/mikifus/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/mikifus/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/mikifus/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/mikifus/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/mikifus/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false}},{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/bcit-ci/CodeIgniter/issues/comments/407085057","html_url":"https://github.com/bcit-ci/CodeIgniter/issues/5542#issuecomment-407085057","issue_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/bcit-ci/CodeIgniter/issues/5542","id":407085057,"node_id":"MDEyOklzc3VlQ29tbWVudDQwNzA4NTA1Nw==","user":{"login":"narfbg","id":1058011,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjEwNTgwMTE=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/1058011?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/narfbg","html_url":"https://github.com/narfbg","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/narfbg/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/narfbg/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/narfbg/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/narfbg/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/narfbg/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/narfbg/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/narfbg/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/narfbg/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/narfbg/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false},"created_at":"2018-07-23T14:50:18Z","updated_at":"2018-07-23T14:50:18Z","body":"Ok, please stop talking about migrations and workarounds ... We have a bug in DB Forge and it has to be fixed; it doesn't matter if you use it with migrations or not, nor are we looking for a workaround.\r\n\r\nNow, on topic - how's it only working with `'null' => TRUE` given that there's no logic for that if you don't pass 'null': https://github.com/bcit-ci/CodeIgniter/blob/b1769f962d74adff766666e2b3e055191bf94b63/system/database/DB_forge.php#L750","author_association":"CONTRIBUTOR","reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/bcit-ci/CodeIgniter/issues/comments/407085057/reactions","total_count":0,"+1":0,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":0,"rocket":0,"eyes":0},"performed_via_github_app":null,"event":"commented","actor":{"login":"narfbg","id":1058011,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjEwNTgwMTE=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/1058011?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/narfbg","html_url":"https://github.com/narfbg","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/narfbg/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/narfbg/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/narfbg/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/narfbg/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/narfbg/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/narfbg/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/narfbg/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/narfbg/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/narfbg/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false}},{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/bcit-ci/CodeIgniter/issues/comments/407110725","html_url":"https://github.com/bcit-ci/CodeIgniter/issues/5542#issuecomment-407110725","issue_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/bcit-ci/CodeIgniter/issues/5542","id":407110725,"node_id":"MDEyOklzc3VlQ29tbWVudDQwNzExMDcyNQ==","user":{"login":"mikifus","id":2385163,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjIzODUxNjM=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/2385163?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/mikifus","html_url":"https://github.com/mikifus","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/mikifus/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/mikifus/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/mikifus/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/mikifus/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/mikifus/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/mikifus/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/mikifus/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/mikifus/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/mikifus/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false},"created_at":"2018-07-23T16:03:17Z","updated_at":"2018-07-23T16:03:17Z","body":"Agreed, let's fix this.\r\n\r\nDeeper test lead me to this check which will resolve to TRUE in all cases as per default all keys are set in the array.\r\nhttps://github.com/bcit-ci/CodeIgniter/blob/e83ae5b13504a00b3e8f543f4e232dff4c90a9aa/system/database/drivers/postgre/postgre_forge.php#L131\r\n\r\nI changed the line to this one (after applying the previous patch) and seemed to solve the issue:\r\n```\r\nif (isset($field[$i]['null']) && !empty($field[$i]['null']))\r\n```\r\nI guess this needs to be changed on the PDO subdriver too.\r\n\r\nCan't say for sure if it works in all cases, but worked for mine.\r\n\r\nGlad to help.","author_association":"NONE","reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/bcit-ci/CodeIgniter/issues/comments/407110725/reactions","total_count":0,"+1":0,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":0,"rocket":0,"eyes":0},"performed_via_github_app":null,"event":"commented","actor":{"login":"mikifus","id":2385163,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjIzODUxNjM=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/2385163?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/mikifus","html_url":"https://github.com/mikifus","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/mikifus/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/mikifus/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/mikifus/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/mikifus/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/mikifus/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/mikifus/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/mikifus/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/mikifus/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/mikifus/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false}},{"id":1755636878,"node_id":"MDE1OlJlZmVyZW5jZWRFdmVudDE3NTU2MzY4Nzg=","url":"https://api.github.com/repos/bcit-ci/CodeIgniter/issues/events/1755636878","actor":{"login":"narfbg","id":1058011,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjEwNTgwMTE=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/1058011?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/narfbg","html_url":"https://github.com/narfbg","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/narfbg/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/narfbg/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/user